extendedInfo.description: Do you like running games? You will love Bunny Maze 3D!Evil bunnies have stolen your carrots and are hiding them in their peculiar cartoon-world. Chase them down and save your carrots, before time runs out!In your quest to get your carrots back, you will travel to magical places, meet adorable characters, overcome peculiar obstacles and discover artifacts that will make you Faster, Stronger, Bunnier!So, grab as many carrots as you can, outsmart your enemies and explore beautiful mazes in this fast-paced action game with adorable cartoon-style 3D graphics!Thinking about purchasing the "remove ads" option? Consider Bunny Maze HD! Bunny Maze HD has hi-def visuals, does not contain any ads and could be even more affordable than "remove ads"!This version is completely Free to play. Gather enough stars by playing through the game and you will be able to unlock all worlds!Spread the word! Bunny Maze 3D supports the iPhone, iPod Touch and Kindle Fire! It is also Xperia PLAY optimized!Help us add new levels: submit your review and tell your friends about the game!Join us on facebook and learn cool tips and tricks!http://www.facebook.com/bunnymaze3d
